description: Blox, Inc. explores for and develops mineral properties in West Africa. The company primarily explores for gold and diamond deposits. The company has interests in Pramkese, Osenase, and Asamankese properties situated in Ghana. Blox, Inc. has a strategic alliance agreement with Ashanti Sankofa Inc. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in New York, New York. Blox, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Waratah Investments Ltd.
